Folder overview
===============

This folder contains all IDL routines needed to run a non-parametric dark matter mass modelling scheme on spherically symmetric astrophysical systems with N tracer stars.

MCMC_nonpara.tar.gz: 	 original version by Dave von Rickenbach

spherical_clean.batch:	 batch job file to fit only up to where sigma is given
spherical_clean.pro:	 MAIN program

spherical_clean1.batch:  batch job to fit whole range, approximate M(>r_outer) by linear function
spherical_clean1.pro:    MAIN program


plot_spherical.batch:	 batch script to compile and start plotting program
plot_spherical.pro
plot_spherical1.pro

helper functions:

arraydump.pro
betar.pro
contourmemfast.pro
gettok.pro
mr.pro
mymakecolour.pro
numlines.pro
nu.pro
oploterror.pro
readcol.pro
reverse.pro
setcommon.pro
sigma_r1.pro
sigma_r.pro
strnumber.pro


working on examples:

sphericalmethod_data
sphericalmethod_output
